No. 26,

Original.

Louisiana v. Katzenbach, Attorney General. Jack P. F. Gremillion, Attorney General of Louisiana, Harry J. Kron, Jr., Assistant Attorney General, and Sidney W. Provensal, Jr., on the motion. Solicitor General Marshall for defendant in opposition.

Motions for extension of time for argument in No. 22, Original, South Carolina v. Katzenbach, Attorney General, and for leave to file a bill of complaint are denied.
